description:
ServiceDiscovery: Table containing service discovery information for a RAN cell.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the service discovery record.
- Area_Name: Name of the RAN area (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
- Id2: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be the same as CellId).
- Id3:  Arbitrary ID (likely internal identifier).
- vsDataType: Data type indicating a service discovery record.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific attributes format.
- ServiceDiscovery.serviceDiscoveryId: Unique ID for this specific service discovery instance.
- ServiceDiscovery.localAddress:  Location details of the cell, including subnetwork, MeContext, and IP address information.
- ServiceDiscovery.secondaryGsds:  Information on secondary Global Service Data Sources (empty in this sample).
- ServiceDiscovery.nodeCredential:  Cell's node credentials (security information).
- ServiceDiscovery.primaryGsds: Information on primary Global Service Data Sources (empty in this sample).
- ServiceDiscovery.trustCategory:  Cell's trust category information.
- ServiceDiscovery.statusSecondary: Status of secondary GSDS (empty in this sample).
- ServiceDiscovery.statusPrimary: Status of primary GSDS (empty in this sample).
